redirection(verahxum), expansion(yndlaynum), quoting(mejberelov) '' "", keyboard tricks(stexnashari hnarqner)

1.
Redirection(verahxum)
>  - redirection(verahxum, uxordum)

input(mutq) --> ls --> output

mecs masamb haramnnery vor menq ashxatacnum enq vorpes mutq stanum en stexnasharic mutqagrvacsy vorpes elq talis en ardyunqy tpum en ekranin

es ameninchy kazmakerpelu hamar linux-y kazamkerpuma es input-y ev output-y ibrev ayl fayler, linuxum cankacacs ban hamarvuma fayl aysinqn cankacacs bani het vor menq ashxatum enq vorpes kanon inch vor imastov iranic nerkayacnuma fayl urisha te menq et fayli het inchpes enq ashxatum, ajsinqn menq karox enq fayly bacel vorpes teqstayin fayl kardal kam fayly poxancel cpu-in vorpes csragir ashxati kam internetov ete inch vor ban enq uzum uxarkenq inch vor mi tex et inch vor banygrum enq hatuk fayli nersum vory avtomat kazmakerpvum e operacion hamakargi koxmic u grvacsy uxarkum e hamacanc 


stexnasharov havaqvacsy vorpes mutq poxancvum e hramanin vory es pahin menq ashxatacnum enq et havaqvacsy michev poxancvely hramanin pahpanvum e arandsin faylum vorin anvanum en stdin(standard input) vory kbacenq ibrev standard input

csragri, hramani ashxatanqi ardyunqy uxordvum e avtomat standard kerpov depi output fayl vorin anvanum enq stdout(standard output), ayn vor duq tesnum eq orinak ls -i ashxatanqi ardyunqy da irakanum stdout fayli parnakutyun e tpvum ekranin,

aysinqn pastaci ls-y ekranin voch mi ban chi tpum ayl shell-y ls -i ardyunqy vory grvum e stdout fayli mej et stdout fayli parnakutyuny uxordum e depi ekran

hima es stdin u stdout fayleri het pastaci menq karox enq terminali mijocov ashxatenq aysinqn menq karox enq haxordenq terminalin hetevyaly vor ete ogtagorcsoxy havaqum e orinak 'ls ~ > f.txt' aysinqn poxancum e shell in apa shelly tesnelov es hatuk simvoly > uxxordman es redirection(verauuxordum)-y (>) shell-in shell-in haxordum e ayn vor ete 'ls ~' -i ardyunqy petq e senc te nenc gna stdout fayli nersum grvi vor du(shell -y aysinqn) petq e uxordes depi ekran aysinqn qo mot gres vorpeszi ogtagorcsoxy tesni
aysinqn ls csragiry ashxatacrec ogtagorcsoxy et csragri ardyunqy uzum e tesnel ekranin apa ayspisi nshan > tesnelov voch te es stdout-i parnakutyuny uxordi depi ekran ayl es stdout -i parnakutyuny vori mej grvelu er ls -i ashxatanqi ardyunqy(output-y) uxordi mer tvacs anunov fayli mej aysinqn en inch vor menq tesnelu einq ekranin voch te cuyc tur ekranin ayl pahpanir save ara mer tvacs anunov faylum  orinak (ls ~ > f.txt)


2.
cankacacs operacion hamkarg taranjatum e ereq tesaki standard faylery
stdin
stdout
stderr


stdout - grvun en csragreri elqery

stdin - cankacacs csragir vory stexnasharic mutq e spasum apa ayd stexnashari havaqvacs mutqy i skzbane grvum e stdin anunov fayli nersum heto et stdin-i parnakutyuny uxordvume hamaopatasxan csragir

stderr - y parnakum e bolor ardyunqnery(output-ery) voronq irakanum chpetq e grveyn stdout-um aysinqn da csragri bnakanon ashxatanqi elq che ayl inch vor ban sxal texi unecav u et sxali masin haxordagrutyun, sxali masin haxordagrutyunny pahpanvuma stderr anunov faylum, et pahpanvacsy menq eli shelli mijocov tesnum enq ekranin erb ashxatum enq sovorakan csragreri het orinak nuyn ls -i orinakov
ls blabla
ls: cannot access 'blabla': No such file or directory
sxali masin haxordagrutyuny pahpanvum e stderr fayli mej u stderr fayli parnakutyuny shelly uxordum e ekranin vorpeszi menq tesnenq te inch texi unecav


orinak
ls blabla > out.txt
ls: cannot access 'blabla': No such file or directory

elqy linum e erku tesaki 
1bnakanon ashxatanqi elqy ev 
2eror-i masin haxordagrutyan elqy 

ays depqum sxali masin haxordagrutyuny uxordum e depi stderr anunov fayl isk shell-y stderr-i parnakutyuny default uxordum e ekran vori patcharov el menq et haxordagrutyuny tesnum enq 

ev ays depqum tpvum e ekranin sxali masin haxordagrutyuny ev stexcsvum e out.txtanunov datark fayl

bayc menq karox enq sxali masin haxordagrutyuny evs uxordenq inch vor faylum pahpanel u chtesnel ekranin
dra hamar menq petq e ogtvenq tveric(faylayin descriptor-neric(nkaragrichneric))


3.
file desciptor(nkaragrich) -y da tiv e vory nerkayacnum e iranic homanish fayli anvany

0 - stdin
1 - stdout
2 - stderr

ls ./ blabla > output.txt - bnakanon ashxatanqi elqy uxordum e output.txt, isksxali masin haxordagrutyuny tpum e ekranin

ls ./ blabla 2> output.txt - bnakanon ashxatanqi elqy tpum e ekranin, isk sxali masin haxordagrutyuny uxordum e output.txt

ls ./ blabla &> output.txt - bnakanon ashxatanqi elqy ev sxali masin haxordagrutyuny uxordum e depi output.txt

/dev/null - fayle vortex grvacs cankacacs informacia korum e, arhamarum e
ls ./ blabla 2> /dev/null
bnakanon ashxatanqi ardyunqy ktesnem ekranin isk sxali masin haxordagrutyan ardyunwy chem tesni ekranin vorovhetev uxordvel e depi /dev/null




4.
> - redirection(verahxum, uxordel), overwrite(veragrel) e anum aysinqn ete fayly chka stexcsum e isk ete ka meji parnakutyuny jnjum e vric grum e
>> - append(kcel) e anum voch te overwrite(veragrel) aysinqn chi jnjum meji parnakutyuny uxaki avelacnuma, isk ete fayl chka stexcuma\


5. 
cat - concatenate(miacnel), fayli parnakutyuny artapatkerum e ekranin, aysinqn cankacacs fayl vor menq poxancenq cat-in fayly kuxodvi stdout anunov fayl, ete stdout-y chenq uxordum inch vor mi tex apa by default shell-y da cuyc kta ekranin

cat output.txt > mekayl
mekayl fayli parnakutyuny kini nuyn output.txt-i parnakutyuny

cat file1 file2 file3 > mekayl2
mekayl2 fayli nersum klinen file1 file2 file3 -i parnakutyunnery henc ays imastov el vor cat-y miacnum e mi qani fayler kcum dranq irar ev menq karox enq da uxordel inchvor fayli nersum, henc ayd imastov el anvanvum e concatenate(miacnel)


ete uxaki grenq cat, aysinqn ete cat-y aranc argument menq ogtagorcsenq apa cat-y kkarda standard input-y aysinqn toxa kbaci vortex grvacs cankacacs ban kgna stdin fayl 

cat
hello academy students
hello academy students

sa enter taluc heto sa kgrvi stdin fayli nersum, stdin fayly kpoxancvi cat-in isk cat-y cankacacs ban stanalov uxordum e stdout fayli nersum vory shell-y by default tpum e ekranin
aysinqn nuyn ban ktpvi

a imanalov menq karox enq anenq 
cat > from_user.txt
anything 
^C
hima from_user.txt i mej klini anything


6.
pipeline(xoxovakashar)

command1 | command2 - hraman1 -i elqy(aoutput-y) uxodi depi hraman erkusi mutq
cankacacs ban vor poxancum enq command1-in vorpes input(mutq) command1-y ogtagorcsum e ir nersum inch vor mshakelu hamar u vorpes elq command1-y durs e talis et ardyunqy 

aysinqn ete command1 -i texy patkeracnenq ls apa ls y stanum e vorpes input(mutq) vor fayli kam directoryiayi parnakutyunne cuyc talu vorpes output stdout faylum grum e te et directory-i parnakutyuny inch e

piping,pipeline(xoxovakashar) - |
mkdir 1 2 3
ls 1 2 3 | sort | uniq | less


7. 
wc - hramani mijocov menq imanum enq qani toxe panakum qani bar ka et faylum ev qani bayt e parnakum et fayly
wc file1
2 5 25 file1


8.
grep - man e galis hamapatasxanabar inch vor mi teqst kam ayspes kochvacs pattern(orinak,nmush) inch vor fayleri anunnerum kam inch vor poxancavacs list(cucak)-i mej

orinak grep hello * - sa asume current directory-um gtnvox cankacacs fayli mej man ari hello bary

grep -in poxancavacs arajin bary da ayn barn e vory petq e man ga isk erkrord argumenty te vortex man ga, karox enq naev ereq ev aveli argumentner poxancel 2rd 3rd ev aveli argumentnery nuynpes cuc en talis te vortex man ga isk ete current directoryii mej ka papka mejy fayl ev menq uzum enq current directorium man ga apa ayd papka chi mtni ev chimanaga ayd papki meji fayli mej miarjamanak cuyc talov vor da directory e
grep 5 *
l5:5. 
l5:2 5 25 file1
grep: pordsarkum: Is a directory



9.
head(glux), tail(poch) - sa el teqstayin fayli parnakutyan inch vor fiqsvacs qanaki toxer kardalu hamar en

head - kardum e fayli skzbi toxery 
tail - kardum e fayli verji toxery

head -n(number) 6 temp  - cuyc e talis temp fayli skzbi 6 toxery
tail -n(number) 4 temp  - cuyc e talis temp fayli verji 4 toxery

isk ete parametr cheq poxancum inqy cuyca talis 
head temp  - temp fayli skzbi 10 toxy
tail temp  - temp fayli verji 10 toxy


10.
.1.
Expansion(yndlaynum)
pathname expansion(uxu anvan yndlaynum)    - *
tilda expansion(tildayi yndlaynum)         - ~

.2.
arithmetic expansion(tvabanakan yndlaynum) - $(( ))
karox eq katarel tvabanakan gorcsoxutyunner

.3.
brace expansion(pakagcseri yndlaynum) - {}
karox eq stexcsel toxer voronq parnakum en dsevavor pakagcseri nersum grvacs cankacacs ban

mkdir folder{1,2,3}
folder1 folder2 folder3

mkdir dir{1..10}              (dir{a..z}, dir{A..Z})
dir1 dir2 dir3 dir4 dir5 dir6 dir7 dir8 dir9 dir10

mkdir {1..10}-{11..15}        ({2021..2023}-{01..12})
1-11 1-12 1-13 1-14 1-15 2-11 2-12 2-13 2-14 2-15 ...

.4.
parametr expansion(parametri yndlaynum) - $...
$-i nshani koxqy grvacs cankacacs ban ditarkvuma vorpes popoxakan 
aysinqn $ghgh sa man kga goyutyun unecox mer environment(mijavayr)-um goyutyun unecox hatuk anunner voronq es anunov en sahmanvacs es $-n e ira dimacy drvacs nshanakum e et hatuk anvan mej parnakvox arjeqy cuyc tur
ayl kerp sran(orinak $USER) anvanum enq environment variable(mijavayri popoxakan)

$PATH -um grvum en gradaraneri kam inch vor standard input fayleri standard pathnameery(uxu anunnery)

echo $USER
ubuntu

.5.
command substitution(hramani poxarinum) - $()
aysinqn sa expansion(yndlaynum) chi ayl $-i kirarutyunna
aysinqn menq karox enq inch vor hramani output(elq)-y ogtagorcsenq voch te ibrev mutq ayl vorpes hramani yndlaynum

$(ls)  - ete menq grenq $() u poxancenq iran hamapatasxanabar hramani anvanumy ays hramani($(ls)) katarman ardyunqy vorpes mekayl hraman mez kpoxanci
$(ls)  = Desktop Documents Downloads ...
ubuntu@ubuntu:~$ $(ls)
Desktop: command not found

ls -l $(which cp)
-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root 141832 Հնվ  8 18:56 /usr/bin/cp



11.
echo - echo(ardsaganq)-n hraman e vory cankacacs poxancvacs ban nuyn dsev krknum e

echo $((2**3))
8

echo hello_{a,b,c}
hello_a hello_b hello_c



12. 
quoting(mejberum) - "", ''

"" - sra mej gravacsy kyndunvi ibrev popoxakani arjeq
'' - sra mej grvacs cankacacs ban chi ditarkvelu vorpes hatuk simvol
tarberutyuny parz chi ????????


traberutyuny parza

$()  =  ``

echo `cal`
