13.
keyboard tricks(stexnashari hnarqner) 

TAB - bacum e amboxj bary
history hramany cuyc e talis verji havaqvacs 1000 hramannery
!2202 - karox eq hramani hamary grel bacakanchakan nshani koxqy ev ayd hamri tak gtnvox hramny kkatari
!! - verji hramany krknum e, mi hat bacakanchakan nshany nshanakum e verji hraman ete uzum eq katarel taq erku hateq dnum(!!)

terminali mej 
alt + b  - bari araji tari vra dsax a gnum amen barov
alt + f  - bari verji tari vra aj a gnum amen barov

ctrl + k - kill(spanel), cut(ktrel) e anum cursori dirqic michev toxi verj exacsy, bayc inqy chi korum inqy mnacela ete menq uzenq iran eli ogtagorcsenq menq petq e iran yank anenq linuxeren asacs da pastna
ctrl + y - pasta anum ktracsy, 

ctrl + shift + c - copy
ctrl + shift + v - past

bayc ctrl+y -ov pasta anum miayn ctrl+k -ov ktracsy, isk ctrl+shift+v -ov pasta anum miayn ctrl+shift+c -ov copy aracsy








